      1. Copy Resources/SharedResource.resx to Resources/SharedResource.<culture>.resx
         (e.g. SharedResource.zh-CN.resx) and translate the <value> elements.
      2. Add the culture code to "Localization:SupportedCultures" in appsettings.json.
